-- Classes: PRIEST, CLERIC, TEMPLAR, INQUISITOR, DRUID, WARDEN, FURY, SHAMAN, MYSTIC, DEFILER
--
-- Why: Bot::GetNewSpells() bins class spells by spells.spell_type. Anything
--      tagged 'Unset' is never picked by the brain (default branch returns 0)
--      so wards, group buffs, reactive heals, etc. exist on the bot's spell
--      list but never fire. Recategorizing pulls them into buff_spells /
--      hot_ward_spells / etc. where ProcessOutOfCombatSpells can find them.
--
-- Rollback: see DOWN section.
--
-- Apply with:
--   docker exec -i docker-mysql-1 \
--     mariadb -ueq2emu -p"$MARIADB_PASSWORD" eq2emu < FILE

